In SuryaHadoopPro.jar i am providing five simple examples for MapReduce Programming. 
Extract SuryaHadoopPro.jar for Source Code, and Import them into Eclipse.
Using jar file you can run these Applications in Psuedo Cluster Mode.
Extract inputs.tar.gz for the following input files.

1. SED - 
   input - /inputs/input1.txt

2. GREP -
   input - /inputs/input1.txt

3. Longest
   input - /inputs/longest.txt

4. AverageCount
   input - /inputs/avgcount.txt

5. Alphabets is the example for Partitioner
   input - /inputs/alphabets.txt
